In a large bowl, whisk together @olive oil{3 tbsp} and @ground turmeric{Â½ tsp} until combined. Let sit for about 30 seconds to let turmeric dissolve. Add @granulated sugar{150 grams}, @lemon zest{2 whole lemons}, room temperature @cream cheese{114g}, room temperature @egg{1 large}, and @vanilla extract{1 tsp}. Vigorously whisk to combine and aerate the mixture, about 1 minute.

